1. At line 830: `serviceCache->put(result->actualDescriptor, result, status);` - this is in `ICUService::getKey` and after this call, if U_FAILURE(status), it does `delete result;` at line 832.

2. At line 839: inside a loop, it also calls `serviceCache->put(*desc, result, status);` and if U_FAILURE(status), it also does `delete result;` at line 841.

